Party Night slot-machine has five reels and twenty paylines where 1 to 5 coins can be wagered per line! The game has Scatter symbol, three or more Scatters anywhere on the reels will activate free spins! This slot game incorporates Bonus symbol, the combination of at least 3 of them will trigger the bonus game! There is also Wild symbol that substitutes for any symbol in the game except Scatter and Bonus to comlete the winning combination! The game features MEGAWILD, when all the symbols on the reel become wild - thus, chances of winning are tripled! Enjoy the party and get ready for surprises!